{"tid":202303,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"【打死唔搬】兩姊妹愛梅窩棄市區工作 開店賣炸雞髀街坊叫好","createTime":"2017-04-15T11:42:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-16T10:32:20.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b776df8ab68da37d6fa9ae4034d97135238c2344","tid":202303,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T11:42:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170414/large/1492153315_6eff.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170414%2Flarge%2F1492153315_6eff.jpg&h=4f715fab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n記者來到梅窩一間小食店，店主兩姊妹自小於大嶼山長大、嫁到梅窩十多年又從未住過市區。家姐歐陽詩敏跟我分享市區人對離島居民生活的疑問時，沒好氣地說：「我不明白這麼多年都會有人問梅窩有無麥當勞、惠康同7仔，以為我們資源好缺乏，其實這裏通通都有！只是想買對波鞋同名牌衣物，就真的沒有了。」妹妹歐陽詩慧附和說：「我以前在銅鑼灣返工，同事聽到我住梅窩就問我點返工？咁遠？車到不到？其實我返工比住上水、元朗的同事更快，只是他們住新界，我就相隔個海同島罷了。」上年歐陽姐妹先後辭去市區的工作，在梅窩村內經營了小食店，賣的小吃並不太特別，不過是車仔麵、燒賣腸粉和炸雞髀之類，卻正是梅窩街坊欠缺的。炸雞髀是招牌貨，用自家調製的炸粉即叫即生炸，需時20分鐘， 吃下去皮薄香脆不油膩，十分好吃。<br />\n<br />\n父親離世　為母有寄託　　<br />\n小店人手有限，賣清後就收舖，朝8經營至下午4時，一來方便兩姐妹照顧家庭，二來不希望來幫手的媽媽辛苦。原來開舖的其中一個原因是爸爸離世後，想讓媽媽有一個寄託。兩姊妹異口同聲說：「爸爸因病突然離世，當時開舖是希望媽媽不要獨留家中，望住四道牆胡思亂想。」開舖後，媽媽有個聚腳點，生活亦有所寄託。現時兩姐妹非常享受梅窩的生活，從未打算搬出市區。可能有人會說市區的資源較豐富，師資亦較良好，對小朋友將來發展更好，兩孩之母的家姐說子女不喜歡人煙稠密的市區，可是梅窩沒有中學，兒子日後也要到市區上學；妹妹則說小朋友長大後，一家不會搬離梅窩，因為不想小朋友為讀書而失去親近梅窩大自然的機會。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/supplement/20170415/56564119\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fsupplement%2F20170415%2F56564119&d=lEFZiSwVnaVog3Ki0s%2BD%2FzCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=de8db734\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fsupplement%2F20170415%2F56564119&h=e2886232\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/supplement/20170415/56564119</a>"},{"pid":"a46d156e4ff595f31a74c7280b5241df9027934d","tid":202303,"uid":12034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T11:46:18.000Z","msg":"食到居屋條水仲走咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecc225458aa5128bd1098e8306e3e8ba779b854e","tid":202303,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T14:23:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa5a52d1da7387202b2ae8de43dbfc88f29be035","tid":202303,"uid":38651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T15:51:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食到居屋條水仲走咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n遲啲肯定多好多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34183b83b96ae37b517c5dccc35536f1c3319fc9","tid":202303,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T17:01:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d9fa0486ce2823acbf940066e44c94c56b4a261","tid":202303,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T01:54:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>食到居屋條水仲走咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n遲啲肯定多好多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27aedfe2325d165a019126c2e203dfd2cc6fec34","tid":202303,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T01:56:00.000Z","msg":"獨市生意仲會走咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee33aef68ab83cb3ed7adab985d20f24dfeb9675","tid":202303,"uid":103127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T06:11:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cd7f6c069ab1b67271b15570c6dbf5d7d67b3175","tid":202303,"uid":32723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T09:01:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去梅窩物色定間鋪賣雜貨和野食都好，遲幾年有咁多人入來住</blockquote><br />\n起埋居屋<br />\n<br />\n佢開埋夜晚啦<br />\n<br />\n放工返屋企前買隻脾做餸<br />\n<br />\n或食個車仔麵又得"},{"pid":"72b1c73acd3e1e906b7d3f549bfe19d310d70d42","tid":202303,"uid":56453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T10:04:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>食到居屋條水仲走咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n遲啲肯定多好多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n特登入梅窩食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fba72e0137434fef736c9f06be48d4dfa5a381b","tid":202303,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T10:32:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}